##Currently only officially supported on Debian Linux

To install, get Bundler (`gem install bundler`) and then install the required gems using `bundle install`.

To start the bot, run `start.rb`.

A sample SQL file (triviabot.sql) is included in this respository to quickly setup a database, but only includes a few sample questions.

Note: the MySQL2 gem requires libmysqlclient-dev to be installed.
